        @GET
 @Path(value="mdata")
BiboxResponse<BiboxOrderBook> orderBook(@QueryParam(value="cmd")
                                                                     String cmd,
                                                                     @QueryParam(value="pair")
                                                                     String pair,
                                                                     @QueryParam(value="size")
                                                                     Integer size)
                                                              throws IOException,
                                                                     BiboxException
        Retrieves the order book for a currency pair.
        参数:
        cmd - always "depth"
        pair - the currency pair
        size - the max size of the order book (1-200)
        返回:
        抛出:

        BiboxException
